<section class="mb-8">
    <div class="leading-relaxed text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-justify space-y-2">
        <p>Hi,</p>
        <p>I'm a passionate software engineer from Kerala. I absorb and emit a lot of JavaScript, and when I'm not coding, I'm usually tinkering with IoT and electronics â€” if it has wires, buttons, or blinking lights, I'm in.</p>
        <p>I appreciate all forms of art, from choosing the perfect font color to turning my space into a mini jungle with plants. I also enjoy capturing subtle moments that people often overlook.</p>
